text: Aminata Touré (12 December 1952 – 12 January 2022) was a Guinean politician. She was mayor of Kaloum from 2018 until her death in 2022. Touré died in Morocco from a long illness, on 12 January 2022, at the age of 69. ==References== Category:1952 births Category:2022 deaths Category:Guinean politicians Category:Mayors
title: Aminata Touré (Guinean politician)
